<div id="container_3">
     <h2> CASE STUDY: Product Research</h2>
        <h3> Case Study 1: Evergreen Product</h3>
  <div class="case_study">
       <div> <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/Shoe-rack-Trend-Analysis.png?raw=true" alt="analysis">
       <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/Shoe-rack-PPSpy.png?raw=true" alt="PPSpy"> </div>
      <div>
        <p class="case_desc">Sample Evergreen Product: Shoe rack</p>
        <p class="case_desc">Shoe rack shows a search trend that remains steady over the years, classifying it as an evergreen product suitable for long-term store stability and consistent ad campaigns.
</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li> Price Range: USD 56.99–601.96
</li>
          <li>Monthly sales: 20-280 sales
</li>
          <li>Monthly Revenue: USD 11.9K–16.9K
</li>
          <li>Last Sale Dates: Active as of October 2025
</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="case_desc">These figures show steady product sales across multiple sellers, proving that the item sustains long-term performance rather than short-term hype.
</p>
      </div> 
      </div>
    <div class="case_study">
       <div> <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/shoerack-suppliers-price.png?raw=true" alt="supplier_price">
       <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/sho-rack-meta-ad.png?raw=true" alt="meta-ad"> </div>
      <div>
        <p class="case_desc">In this case for a 3-tier Shoe having 209 monthly sales, it is found to be profitable with the same product selling at Aliexpress and Alibaba for lower prices.
</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li> Average Cost: USD 4–16 per unit
</li>
          <li>Shipping (estimate): USD 5–10
</li>
          <li>Retail Price: USD 56.99
</li>
          <li>Estimated Gross Profit: ~$30–$40 per sale (around 70–80% margin)
</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="case_desc">Strong profit margin allows room for paid advertising while still maintaining healthy ROI. The product also shows 77 active sales in Meta Ad Library, indicating consistent demand and ad performance.
</p>
      </div> 
      </div>

  <h2> CASE STUDY: Product Research </h2>
        <h3> Case Study 2: Seasonal Product</h3>
  <div class="case_study">
       <div> <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/christmas_decor_trend_analysis.png?raw=true" alt="analysis">
       <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/Christmas-decor-PPSpy.png?raw=true" alt="PPSpy"> </div>
      <div>
        <p class="case_desc">Sample Evergreen Product: Shoe rack</p>
        <p class="case_desc">Product Research: Christmas Decor (Seasonal Product Discovery)Christmas-themed product show a strong rise in sales during the last quarter of the year, classifying them as seasonal products ideal for short-term campaigns and festive promotions.

</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li> Price Range: USD 14.99–38
</li>
          <li>Monthly Sales: 173–311 sales
</li>
          <li>Monthly Revenue: USD 2.6K–7.6K
</li>
          <li>Last Sale Dates: Active as of October 2025
</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="case_desc">Data indicates a strong seasonal spike in engagement and sales for Christmas decor, making it a profitable product category for short-term campaigns during the festive period. These items perform best when launched ahead of the holiday rush, supported by visually appealing and emotion-driven marketing.

</p>
      </div> 
      </div>
    <div class="case_study">
       <div> <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/decor-prices.png?raw=true" alt="supplier_price">
       <img class="case" src="https://github.com/krisnadashkc/Portfolio-photos/blob/main/decor-meta-ad.png?raw=tru" alt="meta-ad"> </div>
      <div>

        <p class="case_desc">In this case for Christmas balls and ornaments, the product shows strong market potential with consistent seasonal demand during Q4. Similar items are listed on Shopify stores for USD 14.99–38, while they can be sourced on AliExpress and Alibaba for much lower prices — as low as USD 0.59–0.99 per set.
</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li> Average Cost: USD 0.59–0.99 per set
</li>
          <li>Shipping (estimate): USD 3–6
</li>
          <li>Retail Price: USD 14.99–38
</li>
          <li>Estimated Gross Profit: ~$10–30 per sale (around 70–85% margin)
</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="case_desc">The low sourcing cost and strong seasonal demand make Christmas decor a high-margin product, ideal for short-term campaigns. With 100 active ads in Meta Ad Library, it shows strong advertiser interest and reliable holiday performance.
</p>
      </div> 
      </div>
